data.description: ***SELLER TO PAY $1500 TOWARDS BUYER CLOSING COSTS OR RATE BUY DOWN WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER*** Extremely well maintained 2 bedroom, 2 bath unit with a garage in Victoria Place.  This home is being sold fully furnished and ready for the new owner! New HVAC in 2020, new screened porch in 2020, new Maytag washer and dryer in 2022, and the entire home was replumbed in 2023! The roof and exterior siding were replaced in 2021.   Victoria Place is conveniently located close to Tanger Outlets, OWA, and endless other shopping and dining opportunities. This ground level unit is immaculate! This could be a great investment property, primary or second home. Don't miss out on this exceptional value in Foley! Buyer to verify all information deemed pertinent.
